lead_paragraph: Top-seeded Martina Hingis beat Tamarine Tanasugarn, 7-5, 6-2, yesterday to advance to the Sunfeast Open semifinals in Calcutta, India. Hingis will play fifth-seeded Sania Mirza, who beat Aravane Rezai, 6-4, 7-5.
